text.section:
The commissioner shall promulgate administrative regulations pursuant to KRS Chapter 13A:
Establishing the form and content of a statement for services;
Specifying the manner in which the employee may designate and change the designation of physicians;
Requiring selection of gatekeeper physicians;
Requiring reports from providers on the condition of the employee; and
Establishing procedures by which disputes relative to the necessity, effectiveness, frequency, and cost of medical services shall be resolved.
